            <lg xml:id="TK1261">
<l>vāḷaṟṟup puṟkeṉṟa kaṇṇu mavarceṉṟa</l>
<l>nāḷoṟṟit tēynta viral</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My finger has worn away by marking (on the wall) the days he has been absent while my eyes have lost their lustre and begin to fail.</l>
